  "title": "Accounts Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Note:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>This role will be based on property site</li>\n  <li>Willing to work 5.5 days per week (Monday – Friday, half day on Saturdays)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Issuing of cheques</li>\n  <li>Prepare cash management form weekly</li>\n  <li>Maintain cash book and petty cash</li>\n  <li>Keying in General Ledger and Accounts Receivables</li>\n  <li>Receive payments and issuing of receipts</li>\n  <li>Provide administrative and front desk support</li>\n  <li>Attend to residents’ and owners’ enquiries</li>\n  <li>Other job related and ad-hoc duties</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum GCE ‘O’/’N’ Level</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of relevant working experience in Accounting/Admin preferred</li>\n  <li>Proficient in MS Office applications</li>\n  <li>Meticulous, resourceful &amp; motivated</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Service-oriented and able to work independently</li>\n</ul>",
